{"type": "article", "id": 26552, "title": "极简的黑白灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-09T06:56:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145447eL2o940z5hPyqSxR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><a href=\"http://www.jordiblasi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Jordi Blasi</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.estiluz.com/en/colecciones/aro\">Aro</a> 是一个极简风格的黑色灯具，可以根据需要自由调节。它的主体为圆盘形，通过背面的小圆环不仅能够灵活地上下移动、左右旋转，也能同其他类型的灯柱匹配在一起，变成一盏落地灯或是台灯。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145444ZxQFuwyThCglWOcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145445Te6cIHmyxi1hYkuP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7152381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145445SpLda7ATNmOKhywU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145446hdiKX0N1eLQMxupC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}